00:03:31.033 --> 00:03:31.613
in the denominator,

00:03:31.613 --> 00:03:33.494
from the exponent in the numerator.

00:03:33.494 --> 00:03:36.419
So it's going to be 10 to
the nine minus eight power,

00:03:36.419 --> 00:03:37.476
10 to the first.

00:03:37.476 --> 00:03:39.255
