00:03:39.255 --> 00:03:40.417
Well that's not exactly what they have

00:03:40.417 --> 00:03:42.820
over here, but we see 7/3,

00:03:42.820 --> 00:03:45.919
this is 2 1/3 times 10.

00:03:45.919 --> 00:03:50.919
So we could say this is
equal to 2 1/3 times 10,

